cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.MM, cs.RO 

The paper deals with pedestrian detection using deep learning techniques, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The paper also focuses on learning feature representations using deep neural networks (cs.LG) and proposes a novel cross-modality learning framework (cs.AI). The use of multimodal data (RGB and thermal) also suggests a potential fit for multimedia (cs.MM) and robotics (cs.RO) sub-categories.
